content.comment:
Thank you very much for a quick reply and additional suggestions.

In the latest revision of the manuscript we:
- Replaced “cell types” with “neuronal responses” in the title;
- Updated the abstract to remove claims about the existence of cell types;
- Following your suggestion, added Fig. A2 showing the t-SNE embedding of aligned readouts with the features randomly permuted across the neurons. Similarly to Fig. A1, the plot is substantially less clustered than the one in Fig. 6. The examples of MEIs within clusters also look less consistent in comparison to Fig. 6. In Fig. A3 we show the plot from Fig. 6 as well the two controls side by side for an easier comparison.

